<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Squared-error_distortion">Squared-error distortion</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Rate%E2%80%93distortion_theory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Squared-error distortion">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle d(x,{\hat {x}})=\left(x-{\hat {x}}\right)^{2}}">
