    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle I_{Q}(Y;X)}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/17b344effe68f17f29e7af7832f350d07444656d" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:9.152ex; height:3.009ex;" alt="{\displaystyle I_{Q}(Y;X)}"></span> is the <b><a href="/wiki/Mutual_information" title="Mutual information">mutual information</a></b> between <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle Y}">
