</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/0e654dba3783583f42f24a0423a95f50abee5e38" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:29.304ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle I(Y;X)=H(Y)-H(Y\mid X)\,}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>where <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle H(Y)}">
