</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/bb27c403404c6ae81905817b0a0fbc744e93abfe" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:12.029ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle I(Y;X)=0}"></span>. Alternatively, if the communication channel is perfect and the received signal <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle Y}">
