  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/95143759fbeedea0d931454510cc896fe7567937" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.838ex; width:31.548ex; height:6.176ex;" alt="{\displaystyle R_{n}(D)={\frac {1}{n}}\inf _{Q_{Y^{n}\mid X^{n}}\in {\mathcal {Q}}}I(Y^{n},X^{n})}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>and
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle {\mathcal {Q}}=\{Q_{Y^{n}\mid X^{n}}(Y^{n}\mid X^{n},X_{0}):E[d(X^{n},Y^{n})]\leq D\}}">
